These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, swisher
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
2 different games are played: domino, billiard
1. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the swisher-smoker is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Cigar   | swisher     | dunhill   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Game     | domino | billiard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, musician
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the doctor is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Beverage          | juice     | almond-milk |
| Job   | musician | doctor  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
