The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, prince
1. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the person playing poker is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| Game         | mah-jongg         | poker        |
| Cigar   | davidoff         | prince    |

