.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite
There 2 different types of food: strawberry, zucchini
There are 2 different favourite colors: yellow, lilac
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, horror
1. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person watching horror movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | almond-milk |
| Food          | zucchini   | strawberry  |
| Color         | yellow | lilac     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | horror         |

