House: ranch-style, farmhouse
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery
City: paris, edinburgh
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an odd position##4
3. the farmhouse house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
