.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, roller
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian
2 different pets are kept: cat, horse
2 different games are played: bridge, chess
1. the person playing chess is in an even position##4
2. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the roller is the dutch##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Transport           | roller | train    |
| Nationality   | dutch       | egyptian |
| Pet           | cat         | horse    |
| Game         | bridge    | chess   |

