.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-11::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, project-manager
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, scientific
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, february
There are 2 different favourite colors: green, grey
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
2. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
3. the project-manager is in an even position##4
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
| Job           | accountant | project-manager |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery    | scientific      |
| Birthday           | january      | february          |
| Color         | grey | green       |

