The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the fan of folk is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Music-Genre         | folk        | electronic |
| Hobby         | board-games          | photography     |
| Transport   | roller        | tram     |

 